Package org.sbml.jsbml.validator.offline.i18n

Contains the messages and short messages for the SBML errors in different languages.

Each languages should create a separate folder named after the first part of their locale, like 'fr', or 'de'.

Author:
rodrigue
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SBMLErrorMessage
    Contains the messages for each SBMLError in the English language.
    SBMLErrorPostMessage
    Contains the post messages for each SBMLError in the English language.
    SBMLErrorPreMessage
    Contains the pre messages for each SBMLError in the English language.
    SBMLErrorPreMessage_en_EN_L2V1
    Contains the pre messages for each SBMLError in the English language and for SBML level 2 version 1.
    SBMLErrorPreMessage_en_EN_L3V1
    Contains the pre messages for each SBMLError in the English language and for SBML level 2 version 1.
    SBMLErrorShortMessage
    Contains the short messages for each SBMLError in the English language.
